{"tid":1675088,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特區政府叫台灣不應將事件政治化","createTime":"2019-10-25T15:40:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T16:17:23.000Z","uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7a1d264ce16e598299d6f6393efa8b14ef887789","tid":1675088,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特區政府發表聲明，就台灣殺人案疑犯自願到台灣接受審訊一事，港方已與台方聯繫，就赴台的安排作出溝通。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，陳姓疑犯表示，由於最近就有關個案有不同的法律觀點及意見，需要諮詢律師，確保在台灣可獲公平審訊。特區政府說，疑犯已回復自由，他何時赴台是他個人意願，港方必須尊重亦不能強制，完全不涉所謂「政治操作」。為確保疑犯能順利入台，港方呼籲台方盡快掃除入台障礙，將事情回歸司法處理。<br />\n<br />\n港方重申，陳姓疑犯到台灣接受審訊的意願是出自他本人。對於一個覺悟自省、願意承擔罪責的年青人，台方不應胡亂炒作動機，及將事件政治化，希望台方能務實處理，讓對方有公平審訊、改過自新的機會。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，港方尊重法治，依法辦事。台方須尊重香港奉行「屬地原則」的司法制度，停止誤導民眾，妄指港方對陳案有司法管轄權而不用。所謂「香港不審」的說法，完全失實。港方希望台方拿出誠意，理解及配合涉案人承擔刑責的意願，讓法治及公義得以彰顯。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488279-20191025.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488279-20191025.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN0Ka%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=948c3c8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1488279-20191025.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dfc39ba6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1488279-20191025.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"8a03ccdebefdee912816df3f32497b297b69f3c1","tid":1675088,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"送俾啊Sir一招不死必勝法，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">立即行動</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">拯救三萬警察<strong>避免獨立調查</strong></span>！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1674172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1674172</a>"},{"pid":"fb48f4af46ce5c63c02f5f51200d201f0f589838","tid":1675088,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:17:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">10月26日</span></strong></span><br />\n「醫民同行. 共抗警暴」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">遮打集會1800</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hf293f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhf293f3.jpg&h=48e668cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10月27日</span></span></strong><br />\n「追究警暴  連繫穆斯林<br />\n守護民眾  與記者同行」<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>梳士巴利花園 1500</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvA0quw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvA0quw.jpg&h=7052ebf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">11月2日</span></span></strong>&nbsp;<br />\n「求援國際 堅守自治 」<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">流水式維園集會1500</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cG0fYM3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcG0fYM3.jpg&h=a82afeea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情參閱：<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/march.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2Fmarch.php&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN0Ka%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=e333509a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/march.php</a>"}]}